OL,3,CRugby team's bravery after stopping on
OL,4,Cmotorway to help crash victims
OL,6,FThe squad were en route to a clash
OL,7,Fwith Rochdale Hornets for the Women's
OL,8,FChallenge Shield on Sunday morning
OL,9,Fwhen the crash unfolded on the
OL,10,Fmotorway near to the East Yorkshire
OL,11,Ftown of Howden.
OL,13,FAfter seeing the vehicle leave the
OL,14,Froad, the team's vehicle pulled over
OL,15,Fand players and support staff jumped
OL,16,Fin to help the vehicle's occupants
OL,17,Fescape, after landing in a ditch.
OL,19,FThey also gave first aid and helped
OL,20,Fsteer oncoming traffic away from the
OL,21,Fscene as they called for help.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
