FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774951543
OL,3,CRugby team's bravery after stopping on
OL,4,Cmotorway to help crash victims
OL,6,FNo-one in the crash was seriously
OL,7,Fhurt, although the occupants were
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital for minor injuries.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Hull FC said:
OL,11,F"Following the incident, the team left
OL,12,Fthe scene and went on to claim a 4-20
OL,13,Fvictory in Rochdale on Sunday
OL,14,Fafternoon, progressing to the Third
OL,15,FRound of the Women's Challenge Shield.
OL,17,F"The team and support staff acted
OL,18,Fbravely and calmly when presented with
OL,19,Fan incredibly difficult situation, and
OL,20,Fthe club extends their heartfelt
OL,21,Fgratitude for their actions."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
