OL,3,CRugby team's bravery after stopping on
OL,4,Cmotorway to help crash victims
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Yorkshire Ambulance
OL,7,FService NHS Trust said: "We received
OL,8,Fan emergency call just before 9am on
OL,9,FSunday morning (29 March) to report a
OL,10,Fcollision on the M62 near Howden.
OL,12,F"Two ambulances were dispatched to the
OL,13,Fscene and two patients were conveyed
OL,14,Fto Hull Royal Infirmary."
